ISS slaktas på Köpenhamnsbörsen efter midnattsvarning
Det danska servicebolaget ISS handlas ner med runt 19 procent på Köpenhamnsbörsen på onsdagsmorgonen sedan man mitt i natten skickat ut ett pressmeddelande om sänkt guidning.
06 Nov 2019, 08:42 by Robert Triches

ISS is slaughtered on the Copenhagen Stock Exchange after a midnight warning
Danish service company ISS is trading down around 19 percent on the Copenhagen Stock Exchange on Wednesday morning after sending out a press release on reduced guidance in the middle of the night.
06 Nov 2019, 08:42 by Robert Triches
